'''克里斯托弗·考克斯·克雷布斯'''（{{lang|en|'''Christopher Cox Krebs'''}}，{{bd|1977年|1月30日}}），是一名美国律师，曾任[[美國國土安全部|美国国土安全部]]{{le|网络安全和基础设施安全局|Director of the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency}}局长，任期自2018年11月开始至2020年11月17日结束<ref>{{Cite web|last=Macias|first=Amanda|date=2020-11-18|title=Trump says DHS cybersecurity chief Chris Krebs has been terminated|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/17/trump-says-us-cybersecurity-chief-chris-krebs-has-been-terminated.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118013020/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/11/17/trump-says-us-cybersecurity-chief-chris-krebs-has-been-terminated.html|archive-date=2020-11-18|access-date=2020-11-18|website=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite tweet |user=realDonaldTrump |number=1328852354049957888 |date=November 17, 2020|title=Therefore, effective immediately, Chris Krebs has been terminated as Director of the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency. }}</ref>。

