== 事业 ==
克雷布斯的职业生涯侧重于网络安全和风险管理问题: 他曾担任[[国土安全部|国土安全部]]负责基础设施保护的助理部长的高级顾问，后来在[[微软公司|微软公司]]担任网络安全政策主任<ref name="dhsbio">{{cite web |url=https://www.dhs.gov/person/christopher-c-krebs |title=Christopher C. Krebs |date=2017-09-05 |website=Department of Homeland Security |language=en |accessdate=October 12, 2019 |archive-date=2019-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507233710/https://www.dhs.gov/person/christopher-c-krebs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/><ref name="#2"/>。2017年3月，他被任命为国土安全部部长的高级顾问。2017年8月，他被任命为负责基础设施保护的助理顾问，并承担国土安全部负责国家保护和计划的副部长职责，直到2018年6月15日他被正式任命担任该职位。2018年11月，国家保护和计划局被{{le|网络安全和基础设施安全局|Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency}}取代，克雷布斯继续担任该局局长<ref name="dhsbio" />。在任内，他警告美国公司关于进入中国市场需要权衡风险和利益<ref>{{Cite web|title=美国网络安全官员：中国市场连带风险 企业需权衡利益|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/dhs-china-cyberattacks-20190424/4890133.html|accessdate=2020-11-19|work=美国之音|language=zh|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126234017/https://www.voachinese.com/a/dhs-china-cyberattacks-20190424/4890133.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；并警告英国不要使用[[华为|华为]]的设备<ref>{{Cite web|title=美国官员警告：华为设备长期成本并不划算|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-huawei-5g-concerns-20190515/4919067.html|accessdate=2020-11-19|work=美国之音|language=zh|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127061841/https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-huawei-5g-concerns-20190515/4919067.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

当{{le|凯文·麦克雷南|Kevin McAleenan}}离职后，媒体一度报道克雷布斯被考虑出任代理[[美國國土安全部|国土安全部长]]<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/white-house-personnel-director-told-trump-that-top-candidates-for-acting-dhs-secretary-aren-t-eligible-11571683702|title=White House Personnel Director Tells Trump Top DHS Secretary Picks Ineligible for Job|last=Restuccia|first=Michelle|last2=Hackman|first2=Andrew|date=2019-10-21|website=The Wall Street Journal|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191021185147/https://www.wsj.com/articles/white-house-personnel-director-told-trump-that-top-candidates-for-acting-dhs-secretary-aren-t-eligible-11571683702|archive-date=2019-10-21|access-date=2019-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但他表示对此职位并不感兴趣<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/21/us/politics/trump-homeland-security-secretary.html|title=Trump Running Out of Options for Homeland Security Secretary|last=Kanno-Youngs|first=Zolan|date=2019-10-21|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-10-22|last2=Haberman|first2=Maggie|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118013057/https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/21/us/politics/trump-homeland-security-secretary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月12日，有媒体报道克雷布斯将会被解雇，部分原因是他参与创建了一个CISA网站，以揭露与[[2020年美國總統選舉|2020年美國總統選舉]]有关的虚假信息，这些信息大部分是由特朗普总统及其盟友推动的<ref>{{Cite web|last=Geller|first=Eric|date=November 12, 2020|title=Top cyber official expecting to be fired as White House frustrations hit agency protecting elections|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/12/cyber-official-chris-krebs-likely-out-436342|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116035401/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/12/cyber-official-chris-krebs-likely-out-436342|archive-date=2020-11-16|access-date=November 14, 2020|website=[[Politico|Politico]]|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Bing|first=Christopher|last2=Menn|first2=Joseph|last3=Satter|first3=Raphael|date=November 12, 2020|title=Exclusive: Top official on U.S. election cybersecurity tells associates he expects to be fired|language=en|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-cyber-officials-exclusive-idUSKBN27S2YI|access-date=November 14, 2020|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118013039/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-cyber-officials-exclusive-idUSKBN27S2YI|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|西德尼·鲍威尔|Sidney Powell}}是[[唐納·川普|特朗普]]与{{le|迈克尔·弗林|Michael Flynn}}的律师，他在{{le|卢·多布斯|Lou Dobbs}}和{{le|玛丽亚·巴蒂罗莫|Maria Bartiromo}}的[[福克斯新闻|福克斯新闻]]节目中断言，有一个秘密政府超级计算机程序在大选中将选票从候选人[[唐納·川普|特朗普]]那里转移到[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]那里。克雷布斯回应道，这是“胡说八道”（{{lang|en|nonsense}}）和“骗局”（{{lang|en|hoax}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.factcheck.org/2020/11/bogus-theory-claims-supercomputer-switched-votes-in-election/|title=Bogus Theory Claims Supercomputer Switched Votes in Election|first1=Angelo|last1=Fichera|first2=Saranac Hale|last2=Spencer|date=November 13, 2020|accessdate=2020-11-18|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115032246/https://www.factcheck.org/2020/11/bogus-theory-claims-supercomputer-switched-votes-in-election/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年11月17日，克雷布斯发[[推特|推文]]称“59位选举安全专家一致同意”，“我们所知道的每一个案例，这些（舞弊）指控要么没有事实根据，要么在技术上表达不清。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普阵营于宾州、威州再提新法律诉讼|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-camp-raises-new-lawsuits-in-pennsylvania-and-wisconsin-20201118/5667982.html|accessdate=2020-11-19|work=美国之音|language=zh|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202035130/https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-camp-raises-new-lawsuits-in-pennsylvania-and-wisconsin-20201118/5667982.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普解雇负责选举网络安全的官员克雷布斯|url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/特朗普解雇负责选举网络安全的官员chris-krebs-11605663323|accessdate=2020-11-19|last=Murphy|first=Mike|work=华尔街日报中文网|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118014418/https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%A7%A3%E9%9B%87%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E9%80%89%E4%B8%BE%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98chris-krebs-11605663323|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name = Nakashima/>美国总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]于同日发推文，宣布克雷布斯被解雇<ref>{{Cite news|last=Sanger|first=David E.|date=2020-11-18|title=Trump fires Christopher Krebs, whose agency disputed president's false claims of election fraud|language=en-US|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/11/17/us/joe-biden-trump|access-date=2020-11-18|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118012220/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/11/17/us/joe-biden-trump/trump-fires-christopher-krebs-whose-agency-disputed-presidents-false-claims-of-election-fraud|dead-url=no}}</ref>。特朗普在推文中宣称，他解雇克雷布斯是因为“克里斯·克雷布斯最近关于2020年大选安全的声明非常不准确；大选本身存在大量不当行为和欺诈行为”<ref name = Nakashima>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/trump-fires-dhs-election-official/2020/11/17/97d3fa5c-251c-11eb-952e-0c475972cfc0_story.html|title=Trump fires top DHS official who refuted his claims that the election was rigged|last1=Nakashima|first1=Ellen|last2=Miroff|first2=Nick|date=November 17, 2020|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=18 November 2020|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118041406/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national-security/trump-fires-dhs-election-official/2020/11/17/97d3fa5c-251c-11eb-952e-0c475972cfc0_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久，克雷布斯表示很荣幸曾任该职，并称此前一周已经预料到自己会被解雇<ref>{{Cite web|title=和特朗普唱反调？美国网络安全局局长推特得知被解雇，此前曾称大选举欺诈的说法毫无根据|url=https://m.nbd.com.cn/articles/2020-11-18/1550833.html|accessdate=2020-11-19|work=每日经济新闻}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普解雇美国网络安全局长 指其选举言论“不准确”|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-54983450|accessdate=2020-11-19|date=2020-11-18|work=BBC News 中文|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127021625/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-54983450|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而对于整个事件，一些共和党和民主党的政要均感不解<ref>{{Cite web|title=称美国大选“史上最安全”的官员被特朗普解职|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%A7%B0%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%89%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E8%A2%AB%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%A7%A3%E8%81%8C/a-55648463|accessdate=2020-11-19|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208234210/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%A7%B0%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%89%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%98%E5%91%98%E8%A2%AB%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%A7%A3%E8%81%8C/a-55648463|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

